        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nI checked out this change, and I can see that there are really three commits since 'origin/master', but it looks like Gerrit is only looking at the last one. This is also reflected in the 'Relation chain', displayed on the top-left of the web page -- note the two red '(Not current)' indications. Unlike CodeCloud, Gerrit wants only a single commit, so you really need to squash these three into a single commit.",
